metadata.description:
Get ready for my first NFT drop! I'm super excited to share some of my work with you all. 

I am celebrating my friends by creating postcard NFTs that you can gift your friends. 

### All of then will come with revenue splits between:
- a friend 
- a DAO
- the last winner of gnars.wtf auction at the moment of the post. 

### This first one is going to be: 
- 0xigami.eth
- gnars.eth  
- Last Auction Winner: 0x4322d6B24BdA8AF69dD1014C4F29138F6D794aDA
